Garda Down Under S01E02 (9 September 2015)
Summer arrives in Australia, and while Gardai-turned-forensics officer Peter Crosbie struggles with the heat during a burglary investigation, Dubliner Joe Connolly relishes an opportunity to celebrate Christmas on the beach with his friends. In Kununurra, approximately 1,800 miles north of Perth, Michael Henderson ventures into the Outback to search for a missing person, but homesick Martin Mitchell and his girlfriend Niamh visit an Irish-themed store.
